"<activities/kanban>`, :ref:`vista elenco <activities/list>` oppure :ref:`"
"vista attività <activities/activity>` di un'applicazione."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:32
msgid "Chatter"
msgstr "Chatter"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:34
